      <title>乌克兰在俄罗斯轰炸下努力维持电力供应</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/12/12/1218737983/ukraine-struggles-to-keep-the-power-on-under-russian-bombardment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯继续对乌克兰发动导弹袭击，经常以发电厂等基础设施为目标。这导致乌克兰人即使在严冬也要忍受停电。我们的记者访问了一家发电厂，看看在战争中如何保证电力供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/12/12/1218737983/ukraine-struggles-to-keep-the-power-on-under-russian-bombardment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 20:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
